'''艾絲塔瓦娜·波曼'''（{{lang-nl|'''Estavana Polman'''}}，{{bd|1992年|8月5日|||catIdx=Rutte}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.estavanapolman.com/persoonlijk.html|title=Persoonlijk|publisher=Estavana Polman official website|accessdate=6 December 2011|language=nl|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128064526/http://www.estavanapolman.com/persoonlijk.html|archivedate=2011年11月28日}}</ref>是一位效力於{{link-en|丹麥埃斯比約隊|Team Esbjerg|埃斯比約隊}}及{{link-en|荷蘭國家女子手球隊|Netherlands women's national handball team|荷蘭女子手球隊}}的[[手球|手球員]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.handbal.nl/oranje/nationaal-team-dames/Selectie/|title=Selectie Nationaal Team Dames|language=nl|publisher=Nederlands Handbal Verbond|accessdate=18 January 2014|archive-date=2018-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105231946/https://www.handbal.nl/oranje/nationaal-team-dames/Selectie/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://handball.sportresult.com/HBEM14W/PDF/NED-R.pdf|title=2014 European Championship Roster|publisher=[[European_Handball_Federation|EHF]]|accessdate=7 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213012114/http://handball.sportresult.com/HBEM14W/PDF/NED-R.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

她也曾代表[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]國家隊參加比較年輕組別的比賽，並在2011歐洲女子19歲手球錦標賽中贏得銀牌。此外她還被票選為全明星隊中中衛的位置。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurohandball.com/article/14116|title=Denmark triumph at Women’s 19 EURO|publisher=European Handball Federation|date=14 August 2011|accessdate=6 December 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917080201/http://www.eurohandball.com/article/14116|archive-date=2011-09-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

